keeper or something.

01:08:17.860 --> 01:08:20.922
But I thought that all
the people were paid.

01:08:20.922 --> 01:08:22.130
MANU AMPIM: Yeah, absolutely.

01:08:22.130 --> 01:08:25.020
So you have evidence of--
because there's tombs.

01:08:25.020 --> 01:08:27.100
Because when
somebody has a tomb,

01:08:27.100 --> 01:08:31.010
the tomb is the person--
like a tombstone today,

01:08:31.010 --> 01:08:33.680
it would have the person's
name, when they were born,

01:08:33.680 --> 01:08:35.010
when they passed away.

01:08:35.010 --> 01:08:38.149
But there is a big tomb where
it indicates all their life

01:08:38.149 --> 01:08:40.270
achievements, but
also their titles,

01:08:40.270 --> 01:08:41.630
the titles of family members.

01:08:41.630 --> 01:08:44.180
So we know the titles,
what they claim

01:08:44.180 --> 01:08:45.550
to accomplish in their life.

01:08:45.550 --> 01:08:47.770
And you see that at
that location there,

01:08:47.770 --> 01:08:52.024
there's-- what's been found
is the bakery, the brewery,

01:08:52.024 --> 01:08:55.010
the tombs, their titles.

01:08:55.010 --> 01:08:56.069
So they're all laid out.

01:08:56.069 --> 01:08:58.020
And not only their
titles, but also

01:08:58.020 --> 01:09:03.880
how the-- they call it
a [? zha ?] or people

01:09:03.880 --> 01:09:07.042
translate it as a gang,
not a gang of thugs,

01:09:07.042 --> 01:09:08.340
but a gang of workers.

01:09:08.340 --> 01:09:11.229
How they were organized
to do the work.

01:09:11.229 --> 01:09:13.370
So, usually, they would
work in 3 month shifts.

01:09:13.370 --> 01:09:15.819
And then, they would go
back into their communities.

01:09:15.819 --> 01:09:17.819
So that it was a
public works project

01:09:17.819 --> 01:09:19.760
built by Africans stonemasons.

01:09:19.760 --> 01:09:23.220
And in fact, there was communal,
cooperative, and collective

01:09:23.220 --> 01:09:24.699
public works projects.

01:09:24.699 --> 01:09:25.990
It had nothing do with slavery.

01:09:25.990 --> 01:09:29.285
But those tombs, and the
titles, and how and when people

01:09:29.285 --> 01:09:33.816
were paid, that sealed
the case of '92.

